<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a" n="4">이런 갑갑 일은 업외</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="1">거번 그 喜報 듣고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="2">掃除萬事여 려왇</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="3">손을 대졉 道理 灑掃應對 거시 올흐매</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="4">집 內外 掃除 後에 請게 엳</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="1">사이 너모 몰면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="2">되염즉 일도 몯 될 거시오매</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="3">아마 너울거리가 이셔야 쓰니</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20b" n="1">아모 耽戀酒色여</sent>
